# GeoLens themed-demo seeder data checksums.
#
# Format: <sha256>  <basename>  (relative to /data/demo inside the image)
#
# These checksums pin the exact bytes of every bundled dataset so a rebuild
# detects upstream drift (Natural Earth filename rotation, GEBCO re-uploads,
# UCDP version bumps, etc.).
#
# Recompute after any upstream source change via:
#
#   docker run --rm --entrypoint sh $(docker image ls \
#     --filter=reference=*seeder* -q | head -1) \
#     -c "cd /data/demo && sha256sum *.tif *.csv *.geojson"
#
# Populated: 2026-04-09 (first successful build on this machine)

# ----- Theme 1 rasters -----
88989ea091a3cbf5551c0def8004579649594b39aaae15bdcf0b20bc18693673  gebco_2024_30arcmin.tif
381106ecd970ad6fb9f0a82428b507d3a0ac88366e683208a3ab9f0b2d4a670a  gebco_2024_viridis.tif
2ff4e09c48f13671e89cc604a46245d160b4ac87d8c5b021c2125ad7ae7b098b  ne_10m_shaded_relief.tif
d95ddde5fdfa3a73def60479f91b1899611b381edfc36b99042484629ffa7943  srtm_himalayas.tif

# ----- Theme 2 indicator pre-joins + Manhattan buildings -----
6fba0b33ac7b50e2cc8ed56c2bdccbc4b72f403824343603703571d0fcb4c890  gdp_per_capita_ppp_2023.geojson
9cce62440ffacd7bd026d3547ac64205526807d72892902bf743fe4fe125495a  life_expectancy_2021.geojson
# manhattan_buildings.geojson — excluded from strict checksums because it is
# fetched from NYC Open Data's live Socrata API (dataset 5zhs-2jue) and the
# response bytes vary between builds as the dataset is updated.

